# ArtemisAI – Brand & Style Framework

**Purpose:** Ensure consistent, memorable visuals and messaging whenever ArtemisAI communicates—on the web, in slide decks, social media, or print.

---

## 1. Brand Essence
| Element     | Definition                                                                                   |
|-------------|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| **Mission** | "Democratize cutting‑edge AI so every small business can compete and thrive."               |
| **Vision**  | "A world where access to powerful AI is as simple as flipping a switch."                     |
| **Personality** | Futuristic • Empowering • Approachable • Trustworthy                                   |
| **Tagline** | "AI, unlocked for all."                                                                      |

---

## 2. Logo System
- **Primary Mark:** The triangular glyph with humanoid figure ("Artemis Glyph").
- **Clear‑space:** Minimum: height of the glyph’s circle on all sides.
- **Minimum size:** 32 px height digital / 10 mm print.
- **Color Variations:**
  - Full‑color (gradient or flat)
  - Monochrome light (white) & dark (#1B1643)
- **Don’ts:** No skewing, recoloring outside palette, or placing on low‑contrast backgrounds.

---

## 3. Color Palette
| Role                    | HEX       | RGB         | Usage                          |
|-------------------------|-----------|-------------|--------------------------------|
| **Primary Deep Space Violet** | `#1B1643` | 27,22,67    | Backgrounds, CTA buttons       |
| **Secondary Lavender**  | `#B7A8F1` | 183,168,241 | Accents, gradients              |
| **Accent Aqua**         | `#3EE0C7` | 62,224,199  | Highlights, icons               |
| **Accent Magenta**      | `#FF4BE9` | 255,75,233  | Highlights, interactive states  |
| **Neutral Light**       | `#FFFFFF` | 255,255,255 | Text on dark BGs                |
| **Neutral Dark**        | `#0C0B1C` | 12,11,28    | Background layers               |

> **Gradient:** Primary Violet → Neutral Dark with subtle radial glow.

---

## 4. Typography
| Style         | Font             | Fallback          | Sample Use                    |
|---------------|------------------|--------------------|-------------------------------|
| **Headlines** | _Poppins SemiBold_ | Arial, sans‑serif | Landing pages, hero text     |
| **Body**      | _Inter Regular_  | Helvetica, sans‑serif | Paragraphs, UI labels   |
| **Code/Data** | _Fira Code_      | Courier New, monospace | Code snippets, CLI      |

**Hierarchy**
- H1 48 px / 56 px line‑height
- H2 36 px / 44 px
- Body 16 px / 28 px

---

## 5. Iconography & Illustration
- **Stroke weight:** 2 px consistent.
- **Shapes:** Triangles, circles, hex‑grids, constellation lines.
- **Effects:** Subtle inner‑glows matching Accent Aqua & Magenta.

---

## 6. Imagery Style
- **Conceptual:** Abstract depictions of data nodes, constellations, small business scenes overlaid with geometric AI motifs.
- **Tone:** Optimistic, futuristic but human‑centric (focus on empowerment).
- **Filters:** Deep violet overlay @ 35% opacity for unity.

---

## 7. Voice & Tone
| Scenario       | Tone                | Example                                           |
|----------------|---------------------|---------------------------------------------------|
| Website Hero   | Inspirational       | “Big‑league AI, finally within reach.”            |
| Blog Post      | Educational + Friendly | “Here’s how AI can auto‑sort those invoices…”   |
| Release Notes  | Concise + Clear     | “Added multilingual support; dashboards now…”     |

---

## 8. UI Components (Quick Specs)
- **Buttons:** 12 px radius, gradient fill (Primary→Secondary), bold white text.
- **Cards:** 24 px radius, soft shadow (`0 4 px 12 px rgba(0,0,0,0.25)`), icon top‑left.
- **Inputs:** Dark BG, 1 px Lavender border, Aqua focus glow.

---

## 9. Accessibility
- Maintain WCAG AA contrast (≥4.5:1) for all text.
- Provide alt text for all imagery.
- Keyboard‑navigable interactive elements.

---
